    "We have prepared a Google Forms survey containing inquiries related to gender, age, years of experience, and the highest level of education and requested volunteers, spanning from beginners to experts, to complete the questionnaire without using any additional help.",
    "Next, the 25 selected LLM models filled all the four CyberMetric datasets.",
    "The comprehensive analysis of the accuracy of the 30 participants and the LLMs will be discussed in Section IV.Lastly, an automated statistical analysis is carried out for the entire set of questions.",
    "This is to confirm that all answers are consistent within the A, B, C, and D options.",
    "Additionally, we have taken steps to ensure that the answers are evenly distributed among the options."
